folder: Brookville Boulevard & Edgewood Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Brookville Park (Queens): Viewing southwestward across Conselyea's Pond from near Brookville Boulevard and Edgewood Avenue.
View 2 is northeastward from the same vantage point and shows an old pumping station of the City's department of water supply.

Views 1,2: March 9, 1927

P. L. Sperr
